(64,48,'mfn-page-items-seo','Slider\n\n[smartslider3 slider=3]\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\n<span class=\"themecolor\">Tours destacados</span>\n\n<span class=\"big\">Todo en turismo en Santa Marta con Bessones y Convenio Marsol. <br/>\r\nRNT 34758 </span>\n\narrows\n\nPalomino\n\n<div style=\"line-height: 0; margin-bottom: 20px;\">\r\n	<a href=\"pasadia-palomino\"><img class=\"scale-with-grid\" src=\"http://localhost/bessones/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/SIERRA-DE-PALOMINO.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></a>\r\n</div>\r\n<h4>Playa Escondida Palomino</h4>\r\n<h4><span class=\"themecolor\">desde $150.000</span></h4>\r\n<p>Es el lugar ideal para amantes de la playa, surfistas y amantes del deporte y está justo en la playa de 6 km de largo Palomino.</p>\r\n[button title=\"Ver más\" link=\"pasadia-palomino\" target=\"_blank\" align=\"\" icon=\"\" icon_position=\"\" color=\"\" font_color=\"\" size=\"2\" full_width=\"\" class=\"\" download=\"\" onclick=\"\"]\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nfadeInUp\n\nCiudad Perdida\n\n<div style=\"line-height: 0; margin-bottom: 20px;\">\r\n	<a href=\"ciudad-perdida\"><img class=\"scale-with-grid\" src=\"http://localhost/bessones/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/CIUDAD-PERDIDA3.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></a>\r\n</div>\r\n<h4>Ciudad Perdida</h4>\r\n<h4><span class=\"themecolor\">$980.000</span></h4>\r\n<p>Conoce la Ciudad Perdida, donde el viento susurra entre las montañas de la Sierra Nevada y la neblina le abre paso a la Ciudad Sagrada</p>\r\n[button title=\"Ver más\" link=\"ciudad-perdida\" target=\"_blank\" align=\"\" icon=\"\" icon_position=\"\" color=\"\" font_color=\"\" size=\"2\" full_width=\"\" class=\"\" download=\"\" onclick=\"\"]\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nfadeInUp\n\nPrograma Golf Santa Marta\n\n<div style=\"line-height: 0; margin-bottom: 20px;\">\r\n	<a href=\"golf-sm\"><img class=\"scale-with-grid\" src=\"http://localhost/bessones/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/25golf.jpg\" alt=\"\"  style=\"height:187px !important\"/></a>\r\n</div>\r\n<h4>Programa Golf Santa Marta</h4>\r\n<h4><span class=\"themecolor\">desde $30.000</span></h4>\r\n<p>Nuestro campo de golf Ojo de Agua es la armonía ideal entre naturaleza, cálido clima y juego perfecto.</p>\r\n[button title=\"Ver más\" link=\"golf-sm\" target=\"_blank\" align=\"\" icon=\"\" icon_position=\"\" color=\"\" font_color=\"\" size=\"2\" full_width=\"\" class=\"\" download=\"\" onclick=\"\"]\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nfadeInUp\n\nParque Tayrona\n\n<div style=\"line-height: 0; margin-bottom: 20px;\">\r\n	<a href=\"pueblito\"><img class=\"scale-with-grid\" src=\"http://localhost/bessones//wp-content/uploads/bessones/tay.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"height:187px !important\"/></a>\r\n</div>\r\n<h4>Pueblito</h4>\r\n<h4><span class=\"themecolor\">$345.000</span></h4>\r\n<p>Turista Colombiano: $345.000 P/p  <br/> Turista extranjero: $385.000 P/p <br/></p>\r\n[button title=\"Ver más\" link=\"pueblito\" target=\"_blank\" align=\"\" icon=\"\" icon_position=\"\" color=\"\" font_color=\"\" size=\"2\" full_width=\"\" class=\"\" download=\"\" onclick=\"\"]\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nfadeInUp\n\nTambién te ofrecemos\n\narrows\n\n<img src=\"http://localhost/bessones/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/001-hotel.png\" alt=\"001-hotel\"/>\n\nAlojamientos\n\n<img src=\"http://localhost/bessones/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/002-bus.png\" alt=\"002-bus\"/>\n\nTransporte\n\n<img src=\"http://localhost/bessones/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/005-cocktail.png\" alt=\"005-cocktail\"/>\n\nEventos sociales\n\n<img src=\"http://localhost/bessones/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/004-diamond.png\" alt=\"004-diamond\"/>\n\nBodas en la playa\n\n<img src=\"http://localhost/bessones/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/006-group.png\" alt=\"006-group\"/>\n\nConvenciones\n\n<img src=\"http://localhost/bessones/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/003-globe.png\" alt=\"003-globe\"/>\n\nEcoturismo\n\nStyle CSS\n\n<style>\r\n.page-id-2033 { background: #e8e1ce url(http://themes.muffingroup.com/betheme/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/home_tour_bg.jpg) no-repeat to