a para que disfrute de un gratificante baño.</p>\n<p><i class=\"icon-dot\"> </i>Seguro e impuestos de ley, todos los servicios según reglamentación.</p>\n\n<h4><i class=\"icon-money-line\"></i> Valor</h4>\n<p>De 1 a 12 pasajeros: $ 130.000 por persona</p>\n<p>De 13 pasajeros en adelante: $ 100.000 por persona</p>\";s:5:\"align\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"column_bg\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bg_image\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"bg_position\";s:22:\"no-repeat;center top;;\";s:13:\"margin_bottom\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"padding\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"animate\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"classes\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"style\";s:0:\"\";}}i:1;a:3:{s:4:\"type\";s:5:\"image\";s:4:\"size\";s:3:\"1/3\";s:6:\"fields\";a:16:{s:3:\"src\";s:65:\"http://localhost/bessones/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/cienaga2.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";s:3:\"300\";s:6:\"height\";s:3:\"200\";s:5:\"align\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"border\";s:1:\"0\";s:6:\"margin\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"margin_bottom\";s:0:\"\";s:10:\"link_image\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"link\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"target\";s:1:\"0\";s:5:\"hover\";s:0:\"\";s:3:\"alt\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"greyscale\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"animate\";s:6:\"fadeIn\";s:7:\"classes\";s:0:\"\";}}i:2;a:3:{s:4:\"type\";s:5:\"image\";s:4:\"size\";s:3:\"1/3\";s:6:\"fields\";a:16:{s:3:\"src\";s:65:\"http://localhost/bessones/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/cienaga3.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";s:3:\"300\";s:6:\"height\";s:3:\"200\";s:5:\"align\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"border\";s:1:\"0\";s:6:\"margin\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"margin_bottom\";s:0:\"\";s:10:\"link_image\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"link\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"target\";s:1:\"0\";s:5:\"hover\";s:0:\"\";s:3:\"alt\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"greyscale\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"animate\";s:6:\"fadeIn\";s:7:\"classes\";s:0:\"\";}}i:3;a:3:{s:4:\"type\";s:5:\"image\";s:4:\"size\";s:3:\"1/1\";s:6:\"fields\";a:16:{s:3:\"src\";s:64:\"http://localhost/bessones/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/cienaga.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"height\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"align\";s:6:\"center\";s:6:\"border\";s:1:\"0\";s:6:\"margin\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"margin_b